Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.45,0:00:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳶...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 啊 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.02,0:00:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你冷靜一點說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉？ 現在你們在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.61,0:00:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉 振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.67,0:00:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.88,0:00:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.92,0:00:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.64,0:00:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪裡 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.31,0:00:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在這裏 就在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.47,0:00:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 我又讓你哭泣了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.82,0:01:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.75,0:01:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.15,0:01:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.14,0:01:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不可以的 鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.43,0:01:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說過要保護我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.02,0:01:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.27,0:01:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉... 鴉他...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.59,0:01:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙不是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開他 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.21,0:01:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為在這傢伙的身邊才會遇到這麼危險的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.70,0:01:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉是想要保護我... 所以才變成了這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.04,0:01:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.89,0:02:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 佑就是鴉 所以你會幫我的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.30,0:02:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙...
