Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.09,0:09:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做點什麼吧 你們不都是一樣是未來人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未...未來人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我再生會消耗太多的粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梟在哪裡 鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他死了...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.19,0:09:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是燕雀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你擁有可以看見時空的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:10:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後根據你所看到的 來確定時空 來變成你的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.39,0:10:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是戴著假面的人 不是那個人 也不是鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.80,0:10:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假面？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.56,0:10:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是香格里拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉不會死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.99,0:10:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話 粒子會完全消失
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉也會消失...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣 做些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙都哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能找到可以大量補充粒子的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.95,0:10:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許能做些什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子 那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子是構成所有物質的最初的單位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的物質 所有的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是掌握時間和空間根源性的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這個時代還沒有被發現
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽得懂嗎 雪惠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.31,0:11:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時空裏也應該有的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子的終極點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.67,0:11:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果朝這個點前進的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.77,0:11:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果去那裏的話 鴉就可以得救嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要將那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那張臉...是說收穫為零咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:11:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙外出中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有一個收穫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.17,0:12:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黛拓野不在那個屋子裏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人的鞋子連一雙都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事嗎 不窄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經習慣這樣的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 那請忍耐一下吧 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.13,0:12:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫鳶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥 你說你不去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.73,0:12:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為...車子裏坐不下所有人不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.82,0:12:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且即使我去了也幫不上什麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.14,0:12:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你就和上乃木一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一旦發生了什麼立刻聯絡我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.44,0:12:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 要振作一點 拿出點精神來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到剛才的了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被跟蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現了...吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.93,0:13:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子也在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼...我們正朝哪裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前有量子計畫的基地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 那個老師飆起車來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:13:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要跟丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:14:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 給我好好抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老...老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個大姐往哪裡開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.03,0:14:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.50,0:14:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郡山先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說話 會咬到舌頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個大姐真的什麼都做的出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼停下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆胎了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.46,0:14:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 他們不是要走了嗎 那個隨便亂說的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郡山先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:14:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜一點 內田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慌慌張張也無濟於事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.27,0:15:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.83,0:15:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有跟上來了 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.21,0:15:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裏了 粒子集中的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在這樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊 鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色的雪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人 剛才那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.57,0:15:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼 都聚在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍之轉矩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.10,0:15:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使能殺死梟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.49,0:15:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是鴉 也不是那麼簡單可以幹掉他的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 小鷺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死梟的不是鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會相信叛徒的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鷺 夠了住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要向我求饒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒出息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.29,0:16:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...你們的命怎麼也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把龍之轉矩交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時空和拉庫利瑪一樣還沒有達到臨界點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也正是因為是在這個時空
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍之轉矩才可能成為保持全時空穩定的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想聽你的什麼預測
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要把龍之轉矩帶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是我們龍騎兵唯一的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到連你也會顧同伴情誼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 把生命之光...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:16:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了不要問了 老師 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.01,0:17:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這個人要比表面看起來的要輕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.80,0:17:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們約定好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.56,0:17:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不會讓你過去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...真的是燕雀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.86,0:17:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.95,0:18:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雲都流過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.62,0:18:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不讓你過去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可悲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連戰鬥的方法都忘記了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.02,0:18:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明跟我說了那麼多了不起的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把遙弄哭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.85,0:18:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...你不是人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是 你也是 龍騎兵也完了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體正在恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳶君 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為我看到了那樣的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.54,0:19:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼不能被選擇的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.15,0:19:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不存在！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被什麼人所決定的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是絕對不會有的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我和那個人一起走的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉也能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:19:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼總是能讓我焦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍之轉矩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在拉庫利瑪成為幻影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.46,0:20:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真纏人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.02,0:20:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.23,0:20:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 這麼多粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梟在那裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到遙了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還停留在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.90,0:21:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴遙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.36,0:22:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時空的遙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.86,0:22:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.31,0:22:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該說過的
